<div type="translation">
<head>Translation</head>
<p>A public body or bodies...] according to what was decreed by the Council and the People (set up the statue of) C(aius) Julius Philippos, <term lang="la">v(ir) e(gregius)</term>, father of a senator and of former procurators (or ? a former procurator?), who as curator also of our city acted with goodwill and was a benefactor on all occasions.</p>
</div>
